name: Bobby Danny
description: I am honest man! I am looking for a partner ..possibly for life – I am not interested in players who wants to play games. I am an intelligent, creative, funny, adventurous man who needs a match…I am very very open-minded about many things…I have strong opinons as well…I love to travel & I honestly don’t know where I will end up in my life which is great, I think! I can be spontaneous & crazy too – believe me! Basically, I am looking for a woman who will accept me for me & not try to change me…simple
